{"prompt": "Generate a website for a video game studio. The website should be innovative and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Crimson Forge Studios</title>\n    <style>\n        @font-face {\n            font-family: 'Nasa';\n            src: url('https://fonts.cdnfonts.com/css/nasa');\n            font-weight: normal;\n            font-style: normal;\n        }\n\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #A52A2A;\n            --secondary-color: #8B4513;\n            --text-color: #FFFFFF;\n            --background-color: #1A1A1A;\n        }\n\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            font-family: 'Nasa', sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 1000;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            margin-top: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            margin: 0 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 6rem 0;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            min-height: 80vh;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.8), rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.8)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/A52A2A/FFFFFF?text=CRIMSON+FORGE') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            background-attachment: fixed;\n            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 4rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-shadow: 4px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        #games .game-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 2rem;\n            margin-top: 3rem;\n        }\n\n        .game-card {\n            background-color: #282828;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .game-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(165, 42, 42, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        .game-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n        }\n\n        .game-card-content {\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .game-card-content h3 {\n            font-size: 1.8rem;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .game-card-content p {\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            color: #ccc;\n        }\n\n        #about {\n            background-color: #111;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 4px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        #about h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        #about p {\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            color: #ddd;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        #contact {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding-bottom: 4rem;\n        }\n\n        #contact h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-info {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 2rem;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info div {\n            background-color: #282828;\n            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-info h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .contact-info p {\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            color: #ccc;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 4rem;\n            border-top: 4px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        /* Animations */\n        .fade-in {\n            opacity: 0;\n            transform: translateY(20px);\n            animation: fadeInAnimation ease 1s forwards;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes fadeInAnimation {\n            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n\n        .scale-up {\n            opacity: 0;\n            transform: scale(0.8);\n            animation: scaleUpAnimation ease 1s forwards;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes scaleUpAnimation {\n            from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.8); }\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }\n        }\n\n        .letter-animation {\n            display: inline-block;\n            opacity: 0;\n            animation: letterAnimation 0.5s forwards;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes letterAnimation {\n            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(7) { animation-delay: 0.7s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(8) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(9) { animation-delay: 0.9s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(10) { animation-delay: 1.0s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(11) { animation-delay: 1.1s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(12) { animation-delay: 1.2s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(13) { animation-delay: 1.3s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(14) { animation-delay: 1.4s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(15) { animation-delay: 1.5s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(16) { animation-delay: 1.6s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(17) { animation-delay: 1.7s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(18) { animation-delay: 1.8s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(19) { animation-delay: 1.9s; }\n        .letter-animation:nth-child(20) { animation-delay: 2.0s; }\n\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>\n                <span class=\"letter-animation\">C</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">R</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">I</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">M</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">S</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">O</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">N</span>\n                &nbsp;\n                <span class=\"letter-animation\">F</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">O</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">R</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">G</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">E</span>\n                &nbsp;\n                <span class=\"letter-animation\">S</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">T</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">U</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">D</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">I</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">O</span><span class=\"letter-animation\">S</span>\n            </h1>\n            <nav>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"#hero\">Home</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#games\">Games</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"fade-in\">\n                <h2>WHERE PIXELS MEET PASSION</h2>\n                <p>Crafting unforgettable digital worlds, one frame at a time.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"games\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"fade-in\" style=\"text-align: center; color: var(--brand-color); font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;\">OUR LATEST TITLES</h2>\n            <div class=\"game-grid\">\n                <div class=\"game-card scale-up\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/A52A2A/FFFFFF?text=Game+Title+1\" alt=\"Game Title 1\">\n                    <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                        <h3>Crimson Dawn</h3>\n                        <p>An epic RPG set in a war-torn fantasy realm.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"game-card scale-up\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.3s;\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/8B4513/FFFFFF?text=Game+Title+2\" alt=\"Game Title 2\">\n                    <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                        <h3>Shadowfall</h3>\n                        <p>A stealth action game with a gripping narrative.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"game-card scale-up\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.6s;\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/A52A2A/FFFFFF?text=Game+Title+3\" alt=\"Game Title 3\">\n                    <div class=\"game-card-content\">\n                        <h3>Emberlight</h3>\n                        <p>A fast-paced roguelike dungeon crawler.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"fade-in\">ABOUT US</h2>\n            <p class=\"fade-in\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.4s;\">Crimson Forge Studios is a passionate team of developers, artists, and storytellers dedicated to creating immersive and engaging video game experiences. We believe in pushing boundaries and forging new worlds that players will get lost in.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"fade-in\">GET IN TOUCH</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <div class=\"fade-in\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.2s;\">\n                    <h3>Email</h3>\n                    <p>contact@crimsonforge.com</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"fade-in\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.5s;\">\n                    <h3>Social Media</h3>\n                    <p><a href=\"#\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"#\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"#\">Discord</a></p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"fade-in\" style=\"animation-delay: 0.8s;\">\n                    <h3>Location</h3>\n                    <p>Digital Realm</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Crimson Forge Studios. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Built with <span style=\"color: var(--text-color);\">&#x2764;</span> and <span style=\"color: var(--text-color);\">code</span>.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        function animateOnScroll() {\n            const animatedElements = document.querySelectorAll('.fade-in, .scale-up');\n            animatedElements.forEach(el => {\n                const rect = el.getBoundingClientRect();\n                const isInWindow = rect.top < window.innerHeight && rect.bottom >= 0;\n                if (isInWindow) {\n                    el.style.opacity = '1';\n                    el.style.transform = 'translateY(0)' || 'scale(1)';\n                }\n            });\n        }\n\n        window.addEventListener('scroll', animateOnScroll);\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            animateOnScroll(); // Initial animation check\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}